Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白昨天的麥波 該怎麼辦才好？ 圓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:06.76,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3\pos(1029,105)\fs42}陰天過後的鴨川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以跟你說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太信任她比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭也一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的歸根到底只是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥波沒有拜託我復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛~ 這也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個朱比豬頭說了那麼過分的話喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維拉朱力歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她卻處處庇護那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然對幫忙報仇的我發飆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說這是我的啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是該拘束起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是出於何種理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天麥波的行動我想能夠判定為敵對行為了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,構成Polyhedron的各個星系中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都找不到她的星際註冊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就暗示著她出生於邊境的星球流刑地 烏合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人困惑的是那個星球沒有批准
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Organ Bal人權條約
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是對她處理不當的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有可能會發展成星際外交問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還把她們的通信放到螢幕上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在 雷加利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子吵架 大人規定是不插手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地球不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,VOX AURA出現的異變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界所有的研究機關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都檢測到了不尋常的能量放射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候撒落了整片的花朵是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我請您不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們對於vox也只是一知半解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田所艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啥 豬頭豬頭到底哪裡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維拉朱力歐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長個刺蝟頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很粗魯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服裝的品味也很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為喜歡那種披風的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全宇宙就只有浩大叔一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有另一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥波怎麼會喜歡上這種傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是德梅托里奧的王子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子~~~~~~~？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住 死小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那個人的話肯定能… 不管誰都這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是德梅托里奧的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷．加利特的人民也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的話一定能跟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝瑟魯曼哥哥一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓Polyhedron處於和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個維拉豬頭是這麼好的一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是同一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人在我心中留下最後的笑容是在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德梅托里奧和雷．加利特仍然很親密的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經是久遠的話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然窩在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 聊宇宙的東西聊久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說已經放學了阿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那個比起來 運動服社出動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動了 京乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天料理實習社所舉辦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校內烤鰻魚大會用的鰻魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被魚店老闆誤以為是池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就將鰻魚扔到泳池內了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望運動服社幫忙回收一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然總算抓完大部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喪失戰意的人接連出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 麥波呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不也是社員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 兩個人都能收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點解決完畢吧 蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 圓 在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳池跑步很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（鴨女 fight！ fight！ fight！ 鴨女 fight！ fight！ fight！ ）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交 交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 住手阿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼羞恥的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被哥哥大人罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆 快來幫忙啊 真知子老師也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個阿 京乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象徵髮束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還想著你把它扔到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動服之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討 討厭阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連老師都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為只有麥波會說奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明一點都不想想我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,復仇什麼的 誰也沒拜託你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被自己的感情所蒙蔽耳朵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥波已經清楚地告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是發現自己的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立馬道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神速執行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定這裡再去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 還有多少條
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一條
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒法把胸罩跟內褲換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先換運動服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 圓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等不了阿 因為無論被討厭還是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貫徹對朱拉朱力歐的守護之意的麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs46}差點念對！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是全開運動服之魂阿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻 把重要的東西扔到別處還跟她吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊回到燈塔跟那個孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥波 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小圓 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 圓先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 嗯 那個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈…哈…哈啾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟學校的淋浴比起來家裡的澡堂更好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 小的時候沒進過澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個宇宙漂浮著的所有垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢物 渣滓 絕望的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孕育我的烏合就是這樣的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠只有寒冬 烏雲無時無刻不浮懸在上頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有顏色的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿咧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一起去洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 不好意思阿 能不能拿件浴衣過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們相互猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了自保拼盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能存活下去就很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂事開始就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這個世界除了痛苦還有其他感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到遇到哥哥為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維拉 朱力翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維拉朱力歐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢 教會了我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜悅 痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上他人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是我唯一的生存依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你準備去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有目的地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟小蘭沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確是驅走維拉朱力歐的星球公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你一定無法接納我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是圓不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一聲不響就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓她難過阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為對於她來說 你是家族的一份子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這個回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是家族喔 麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在同一屋簷下吃過飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起睡過覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也一起洗過澡阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在聽嗎 麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了這麼過分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對圓也是...對蘭也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能在這個城市中跟你們在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個也是我想說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的麥波我真的搞不懂。 為什麼？ 圓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我著想 謝謝你 麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你成為我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是就只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其實也想一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在雷加利特 成為家人後一定要一起洗澡啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啦！菈芬蒂王女決定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在決定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以三個人再洗一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這種地方全裸有點太認真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有嗎 超～大的浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就由我第一個先洗囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YA～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來當第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 我也要洗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都很努力阿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這雖然不算獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好意我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種衣服怎可能穿在店裡阿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點丟臉阿…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事阿 小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級女服務生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也…有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小蘭來說有點勉強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不該阻止你出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種衣服要不是有好身材的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在幹麻阿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:00.22,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,ED-CH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.82,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:05.84,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Try！ 永不放棄的決心 就在這個胸懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:11.34,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}不論何時不曾忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.67,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Don’t cry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:20.65,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}約好了 不要獨自一人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.97,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}因為彼此永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:35.20,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}將這份感傷（静靜地承擔下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.38,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}定能變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:41.30,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:45.41,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}現在就笑一個吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:47.54,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:56.00,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}這是自己下的決定 並不是他人的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:59.85,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}用率真的語氣說出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:02.03,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:10.29,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}唱著往常的歌曲 將點滴的勇氣灌注於心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.08,ed-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Yeah！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,ED-JP
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.82,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:05.84,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Try! あきらめない心 この胸の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:11.34,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}忘れないから いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.67,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Don’t cry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:20.65,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}きっと約束よ 一人で泣いたりしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.97,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}いつだって一緒だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:35.20,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}悲しみひとつ(そっと分けあったら)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.38,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}もっと強くなれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:41.30,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:45.41,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}今すぐ笑って!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:47.54,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:56.00,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}誰かのためじゃなくて 自分で決めた気持ちだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:59.85,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}まっすぐな声で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:02.03,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:10.29,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}歌ってよ いつもの歌 一粒の勇気を心に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.08,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(150,500)}Yeah！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來到地球一直有個很棒的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出來就行了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚕嚕嚕嚕嚕 提示
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鴨川海洋世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 回答是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要坐在虎鯨的背上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:39.93,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur3\pos(644,444)\fs50}鴨川羅莉塔
